s0#####SELECT COUNT(*) FROM aka_name AS an, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, movie_companies AS mc, name AS n, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND an.person_id = ci.person_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND ci.movie_id = t.id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND rt.role in ('editor', 'producer', 'cinematographer', 'production designer', 'costume designer', 'miscellaneous crew') AND mc.note in ('(2011) (Hungary) (TV)', '(2003) (USA) (DVD)', '(2006) (USA) (TV)');
